 executive officer will continue to prepare her for a senior leadership role in the company” said harrison charlottebased cocacola consolidated is the nation’s largest independent cocacola bottler operating primarily in the southeast —enjoy cocacola— updated daily mfrtechcom includes featured articles and manufacturing news product releases business expansions acquisitions and business forecasts submitted by our visitors or authored by editorial staff advertise with us contact us phone tech  email salesmfrtechcom  starshoot parkway  lexington ky  join with us  copyright  by mfrtech home sitemap submit news subscribe contact client login james r helvey iii  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in james r helvey iii board member at computer task group incorporated view full profile are you james r helvey iii claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view james r helvey iiis full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in james r helvey iiis network and community follow changes in james r helvey iiis employment and moneyinmotion connect with james r helvey iii through your network of contacts james r helvey iiis executive work history current board member computer task group incorporated past to view james r helvey iiis complete executive work history sign up now age      james r helvey iiis biography mr helvey  was appointed to ctgs board of directors in november  mr helvey is a founding partner of the investment advisory firm cassia capital partners llc which he established in  prior to that he was a principal partner with cmt asset management ltdan international asset management firm he helped establish in  where he was responsible for risk management and portfolio construction mr helvey is currently a member of the board of directors of cocacola bottling company consolidated where he serves on the audit committee from  to  mr helvey was as a member of the board of directors of pike electric inc  read more mr helvey  was appointed to ctgs board of directors in november  mr helvey is a founding partner of the investment advisory firm cassia capital partners llc which he established in  prior to that he was a principal partner with cmt asset management ltdan international asset management firm he helped establish in  where he was responsible for risk management and portfolio construction mr helvey is currently a member of the board of directors of cocacola bottling company consolidated where he serves on the audit committee from  to  mr helvey was as a member of the board of directors of pike electric inc where he served on the audit and compensation committees pike electric was sold in december  to court square capital partners from  to  mr helvey served as chairman and chief executive officer of cygnifi derivatives llc a firm that specialized in commercializing risk management tools developed by jp morgan from  to  mr helvey held various managing director positions with jp morgan including global head of derivative counterparty and hedge fund risk management vice chairman of the risk committee and head of business risk monitoring in the corporate risk management group where he was responsible for monitoring the firms global market and credit risks global head of securities lending group where he was responsible for restructuring and implementing a new risk management system and head of the firms derivatives valuation service mr helvey is also a member of the board of directors of piedmont federal savings bank where he serves as audit committee chairman and a member of the wake forest university board of trustees where he has served on the investment policy committee since  mr helvey is also a member of the board of directors for wake forest baptist medical center where he serves as the chairman of the audit and health sciences investment policy committees mr helvey also serves as a director for verger capital management an asset management firm wholly owned with wake forest university mr helvey earned a masters degree in international affairs banking and finance from the school of international and public affairs at columbia university in new york where he was in international fellow he also attended the university of cologne west germany as a fullbright scholar and earned his bachelors degree from wake forest university graduating with honors and phi beta kappa source computer task group incorporated on    sign up for equilar atlas and view james r helvey iiis full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like james r helvey iii more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in james r helvey iiis network and community follow changes in james r helvey iiis employment and moneyinmotion connect with james r helvey iii through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example james r helvey iii james r helvey iiis connections  sign up now to view james r helvey iiis  connections » j eric pike former chairman president and chief executive officer pike corporation alexander b cummings former executive vice president and chief administrative officer the cocacola company james t benfield former president pike electric llc pike corporation audie g simmons former executive vice president operations pike corporation anthony k slater former chief financial officer and executive vice president pike corporation l glenn orr former consultant medical properties trust inc richard h moore chief executive officer and director first bancorp clifford b bleustein former president and chief executive officer computer task group incorporated valerie rahmani board member computer task group incorporated william h jones former board member cocacola bottling co consolidated popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity